{"tid":1499847,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請民建聯及控煙辦協助解決違法吸煙問題","createTime":"2019-08-24T01:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T15:34:13.000Z","uid":243537,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57c6bee9464636090ed8f8d804f5799adc69760b","tid":1499847,"uid":243537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:36:09.000Z","msg":"我每次返屋企都好心痛屋苑入面班長者， <br />\n佢地經常聚埋一齊暢談時事 世界戰略 <br />\n本黎我個心好歡喜 <br />\n見到一班長者咁精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我發現佢地<br />\n好多都唔知自已違法吸煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正當佢地好堅定討論緊政府點穩健地施政<br />\n執法人員令香港更美好果陣  往往都吐出兩口煙圈  但就係正禁止吸煙標示前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更可悲係附近有非吸煙長者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左令佢地有健康既身體 同令佢地感到有人支持佢地既睇法 例如政府一定冇錯<br />\n<br />\n我已經係8月中電郵控煙辦協助了解屋苑情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   得到回覆表示盡快跟進 , 不過因為我返工放工真係睇唔到跟進情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n係我好苦惱既時間我忽然諗起一向關心長者 定期有不同禮物 活動俾長者既 <br />\n民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長者更健康相信係佢地每位黨員既願景<br />\n我即刻睇返我個屋苑都係民建聯架 <br />\n好野 一班長者健康有救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今早已電郵請我區民建聯議員協助跟進控煙辦如何處理， 待回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然可能會一時令長者誤會而投票時有考慮， 但我相信長者健康呢個美好願景先係議員們既重點 那怕選情告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家不妨多關心長者 以行動作支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e966e6e95649ccae8430b7fd7223b59df12a66b","tid":1499847,"uid":243537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:41:46.000Z","msg":"推推大家今早可能放假既 寫下電郵 <br />\n<br />\n幫幫長者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7a4190b7853644b9020fe9b4adb5043f1339f4","tid":1499847,"uid":243537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"幫幫長者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7e0704476b2c685b8c792f9d05b48bb5d926ca","tid":1499847,"uid":243537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:22:02.000Z","msg":"嘆緊冷氣既你記得都關心長者呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a0def567c277512652830a178bc1f3c557bdd9","tid":1499847,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"推！"}]}